src/operations/.title: Operations
src/operations/.body:
Operations
There are several available operations:

filter(object, path, predicate)
insert(object, path, value)
insertAll(object, path, values)
map(object, path, transform)
pop(object, path)
popN(object, path, n)
push(object, path, value)
pushAll(object, path, values)
reduce(object, path, reducer)
remove(object, path)
removeN(object, path, n)
set(object, path, value)
shift(object, path)
shiftN(object, path, n)
unshift(object, path, value)
unshiftAll(object, path, values)
update(object, path, update)

src/functional/.title: Functions
src/functional/.body:
Functions
Functions below can help to apply operations in functional way:

apply(object, ops)
pipe(ops)

src/functional/apply/.title: apply(object, ops)

src/functional/pipe/.title: pipe(ops)

CHANGELOG.html.title: Change Log
CHANGELOG.html.body:
Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file. See standard-version for commit guidelines.
2.3.0 (2019-11-01)
Features

added filter() operation (215e322)
added insert() and insertAll() operations (819b9ca)
added map() operation (bb30de5)
added pop() and popN() operations (b2b6a23)
added push() and pushAll() operations (d7a527c)
added reduce() operation (d4fe4bb)
added removeN() operation (0dce914)
added shift() and shiftN() operations (e0ff8e6)
added unshift() and unshiftAll() operations (9c47290)

Bug Fixes

fixed remove() operation to not create intermediate items (ad32ea5)
fixed README auto-generation (437b628)

Improvements

refactored generate-readmes.js helper a bit (7ada431)

2.2.0 (2019-10-21)
Features

added functional helpers (pipe() and  apply()) (9e8f36b)
added partial application support (6807c8a)
enhance operations to return frozen object (5ae2547)

2.1.0 (2019-10-20)
Features

exported update() operation (c8cc35e)
implemented remove() operation (b72cf7d)

Improvements

extracted update() function (ccfd659)

2.0.1 (2019-10-20)
Bug Fixes

ci: fix publish flow (807988c)

2.0.0 (2019-10-19)
⚠ BREAKING CHANGES

export structure updated

Features

re-implemented basic feature as a set operation (315df41)

Features
